        public void moveToDefaultList(Drone drone,
                     java.util.ArrayList<Drone> oldList)
        Parameters:
        drone - - When the down(decrement) arrow is used in the interface, it will find and remove the drone from that list and add it to the default list so that it may be assigned another task;
        oldList - - The list the the drone was previously in. This is only a parameter to make searching faster, if it makes it easier to use without the list as a parameter then the other method of the same name should be used.
